Document to bring at the embassy for your appointment
  - Passport
  - Your residency document if appyling from outside of India
  - Your past 3 months of bank statement /pay slips
  - Your complete itinerary 
      - your hotel accommodation receipts
            - if you are staying at a host, then a letter from the host confirming the same
      - your return flight details
  - Your travel insurance
      - apporved insurance agents/vendors list is here https://assets.ctfassets.net/xxg4p8gt3sg6/6KaXKp69z2jQ0A0GNURuh/50fac69dd36b8816b407db9ea52aaac9/New_TMI_Companies_List.pdf
  - Fees / cash or check
  - NoC (no objection certificate) from employer
  - address proof
